{"tid":1033631,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"好慘 儲咁耐錢買左部iPhone xs max","createTime":"2019-02-23T10:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T12:24:59.000Z","uid":78533,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee35b1bf95bb431bbe61ddee639015e881ea61dc","tid":1033631,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ＝me.   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =同學  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ＝mk仔<br />\n<br />\n今日比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 串影相連大陸機都不如 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講新機有得先影相後對焦喎 <br />\n點知比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑二手科技 仲要平時唔出聲既死毒撚話佢部htc幾年前就有啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  駁講話得睇移動炸彈爆炸 同比人偷資料啦 解鎖再慢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話爆左再買多部都平過我咁貴買二手科技 解鎖快0.0x秒有撚用 識飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩後尾有個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公屋仔走過黎幫我 屌鳩班an狗 話佢地掃mon慢0.幾秒同冇得用sd野最快既airdrop 功能 班an俠先扮住笑咗走（btw<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做左3個月兼職分期買) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但講真 之前用lgv30 入歌片相都方便好多 <br />\n可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新轉ios未習慣啦 但掃mon的確冇咩lag既 好似係<br />\n<br />\nAirdrop暫時用過兩三次 真係快<br />\n<br />\n想問下巴絲打 iPhone 除左掃mon快外仲有咩好玩野 <br />\n<br />\n同埋bt左d片同舊手機有d無損歌點轉落iphone到?? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有的係咪中左伏 d人明明話iphone 話影相最靚 <br />\n點知岩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎部大陸機出黎影得又大又清 <br />\n連<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />v30果時 影合照夠廣角既優勢都冇埋<br />\n<br />\n定係我信仰唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  比咁貴用落 功能同老豆用緊果部ipadmini4差唔多完全一樣。。。。。 救命！！！<br />\n<br />\n可能有d 1999 但儲咁耐錢想買部功能最好 影相最靚既手機  <br />\n依家真係好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa15dff1e0d03e957f52ec0373da1cea80757d2a","tid":1033631,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:16:46.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒，真係鄧買左i窿個傻仔慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60fcd632d6893395f7ecfe4c7ff9f9e888a1d30","tid":1033631,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb8b0d0d27b23cdbed130373a3001549de577d95","tid":1033631,"uid":78533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d60fcd632d6893395f7ecfe4c7ff9f9e888a1d30","tid":1033631,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"好彩冇燒底板喎"},{"pid":"1010f6363454b5039614765f3488dad2c1cc5a7d","tid":1033631,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c29d745e669f8d514f1b7c7314238874f642099f","tid":1033631,"uid":163783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"xs max 堅唔抵<br />\n<br />\nx 係例子<br />\n<br />\n未夠一年身價跌過半"},{"pid":"9c59b1e51ed2e029125d8b9902613fff61f3403f","tid":1033631,"uid":181294,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1941ca35ae97899038680034e2a3f7b629779a2","tid":1033631,"uid":208553,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"假膠黎講你都算廢<br />\n打d野打到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65a81854bc87e5b71d1b535d9147